      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber">3009.171-8</ph> Ineligible contractors.</title>
      <conbody>
         <p xtrc="P">Any business concern determined to be ineligible for award under (HSAR) 48 CFR <xref outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref "
                  base="Section_3009_171_5_T48_7029101112"
                  href="Section_3009_171_5_T48_7029101112.dita#Section_3009_171_5_T48_7029101112">3009.171-5</xref> to <xref outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref "
                  base="Section_3009_171_7_T48_7029101114"
                  href="Section_3009_171_7_T48_7029101114.dita#Section_3009_171_7_T48_7029101114">3009.171-7</xref> shall be ineligible to receive a contract for guard services under the FPS guard program until such time as:
</p>
         <p outputclass="List1">(a) The concern demonstrates that it has addressed and resolved the issues that resulted in the determination of ineligibility, and
</p>
         <p outputclass="List1">(b) The HCA approves an award request under (HSAR) 48 CFR <xref outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref "
                  base="Section_3009_171_7_T48_7029101114"
                  href="Section_3009_171_7_T48_7029101114.dita#Section_3009_171_7_T48_7029101114">3009.171-7</xref>.</p>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
